{"tid":1245802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行政署基於保安考慮　政府總部明日暫停開放","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T12:45:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1347bf2c1dece9d736a34a94b702b31e450b3b31","tid":1245802,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:43:22.000Z","msg":"行政署表示，基於保安考慮，政府總部明日暫停開放，人員無需返回政總工作，並應按照所屬決策局或部門的應變計劃工作，所有訪客活動亦會延期或取消。<br />\n<br />\n大專學界及網民要求政府下午5時之前，回應撤回修訂《逃犯條例》等訴求，否則將行動升級，包括包圍政總。"},{"pid":"08cbfa564817859c4ed5091e4fa3a313ea101878","tid":1245802,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"仲唔多謝反立法人士？"},{"pid":"731b24c3c1edd63b3b3d7eee1c731439abd2fd2e","tid":1245802,"uid":204352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"狗官s:打牌咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}